<br>
&quot;I haven't taken a single hit yet (though one did try and hit me, but missed)&quot;<br>
<br>
Hits are rare, and usually happen when you get a bit careless, or brazen.  These do often stun, and once they do, you will have 4 of them beating on you for a round or two.  They will take you down FAST, and any skin you have up could be enough to keep you out of the movement reduction health zone, which could keep you alive.<br>
<br>
So no, you don't NEED skin up to kite here, just like you don't need levitate.  But each of these spells just makes it safer.<br>
